sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeGW as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant APIServer as vLLM API Server<br/>(FastAPI/Uvicorn)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Engine as AsyncLLM Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant HFHub as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over APIServer,Engine: === Flow 1: Model Loading (Startup) ===

    APIServer->>HFHub: GET model config & weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN
    HFHub-->>APIServer: Model artifacts (safetensors, config.json)

    alt S3 model source
        APIServer->>S3: GET model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID)
        S3-->>APIServer: Model artifacts
    end

    APIServer->>Engine: Load model into CPU memory<br/>(in-process, Python async)
    Note over Engine: Model loaded into<br/>PagedAttention KV-cache

    Note over Client,OTLP: === Flow 2: Inference Request (Chat Completion) ===

    Client->>KServeGW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Platform auth
    KServeGW->>APIServer: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/8000 (internal)<br/>Auth: API Key (optional)

    APIServer->>APIServer: AuthenticationMiddleware<br/>validates API key (if set)
    APIServer->>Engine: Submit inference request<br/>(Python async, in-process)

    Note over Engine: Continuous batching<br/>Token generation<br/>CPU kernels (csrc/)

    loop Streaming tokens (SSE)
        Engine-->>APIServer: Generated token(s)
        APIServer-->>KServeGW: SSE event (HTTP streaming)<br/>HTTP/8000
        KServeGW-->>Client: SSE event<br/>HTTPS/443
    end

    Engine-->>APIServer: Final response
    APIServer-->>KServeGW: HTTP 200 (complete)<br/>HTTP/8000
    KServeGW-->>Client: HTTP 200<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Prometheus,OTLP: === Flow 3: Observability ===

    Prometheus->>APIServer: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>Auth: None
    APIServer-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>(inference latency, tokens/s, etc.)

    APIServer->>OTLP: Export traces<br/>gRPC/4317<br/>TLS (configurable)
